Prudential’s Thiam to Get 2 Million-Pound Share Award, Sky Says

-- B y   M a r i a   E r m a k o v a
-- 
2011-03-14T12:39:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/prudential-s-thiam-to-get-2-million-pound-share-award-sky-says.html
  Prudential Plc (PRU)  Chief Executive
Officer  Tidjane Thiam  will get just over 2 million pounds under
a company share plan based on Prudential’s performance over the
past three years, Sky News’s Mark Kleinman reported on his blog,
without citing anyone.   The payout will be disclosed as part of a wider statement
on remuneration expected to be made within the next 10 days,
according to Kleinman.    To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Maria Ermakova at 
 mermakova@bloomberg.net  